<subsection><title>Wrap-Up</title>

<p>In this Lesson, we worked on the following skills and goals related to linear models:</p><ul>

<li><p>Identify the slope and <m>y</m>-intercept from the equation for a line</p></li>
<li><p>Interpret the slope and <m>y</m>-intercept in context</p></li>
<li><p>Use the coordinate formula to calculate slope</p></li>
<li><p>Use the point-slope formula to find an equation for a line</p></li>
<li><p>Find a linear model from two data points</p></li></ul>

